            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Place your hand flat onto the <strong>chicken breast<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Slice in half as if you were cutting a burger bun, so you are left with 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> thinner pieces</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid), with 1/2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chicken pieces</strong> and cook for 2-3 min on each side, or until browned</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1581615120347-x200.jpg",
